  x,

  n = 128L,
  sigma = 3,
  weights = NULL,
  upper.hem = FALSE,
  r = 1
)

Arguments

x

object of class "Vec3()", "Line()", or "Plane()".

n

integer. Gridzise. 128 by default.

weights

(optional) numeric vector of length of nrow(x). The relative weight to be applied to each input measurement. The array will be normalized to sum to 1, so absolute value of the weights do not affect the result. Defaults to NULL

...

arguments passed to density_calc()

FUN

density estimation function if kamb=TRUE; one of exponential_kamb() (the default), kamb_count, and schmidt_count().

sigma

numeric. Radius for Kamb circle used for counting. 3 by default.

upper.hem

logical. Whether the projection is shown for upper hemisphere (TRUE) or lower hemisphere (FALSE, the default).

r

numeric. radius of stereonet circle
